类 EditWinnersAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • HttpServlet
      • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.MadnessServlet
        • com.chipsandwaycool.servlet.game.EditWinnersAction
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    MadnessConstants, HTMLConstants

    public class EditWinnersAction
extends MadnessServlet
    This guy responds to the Edit Winners form by assigning the winners of games according to the user input and then asking the business object to "reconcile" the user's selections. This ensures a state of integrity among the whole series of games, since the user might assign a winner to a game in round three but also change the winner of a precedent game, making the first selection invalid. Once all the changes are thus reconciled, they are stored in the database.
